Career Suitability

Your 10th house is about as loaded as a chart gets: Moon (10th lord) + Sun + Mercury (9th lord, luck) + Saturn (yogakaraka), all in Cancer. In plain terms:


Mercury + Saturn together is the classical technology/engineering/analytical-fields combination — strongly validating your B.Tech CS path.
Mercury as 9th lord sitting in the 10th (Dharma-Karma Adhipati-adjacent placement) means your higher education and career are directly fused — your degree is your path, not a detour.
Moon, the 10th lord, sitting in its own sign in the 10th house is one of the cleanest "career will define your identity" signatures in classical astrology.


Job vs. Business

